# Data Dictionary — Dealer Performance Intelligence System

## Dataset Overview
- **Total Dealers:** 500
- **Time Period:** January 2023 to December 2024 (24 months)
- **Total Records:** 12,000 rows
- **Key Performance Indicators:** 11

---

## File 1: dealer_master.csv

| Column | Description | Data Type | Example |
|:---|:---|:---|:---|
| dealer_id | Unique dealer identifier | String | D001 |
| dealer_name | Dealer business name | String | AutoWorld 1 |
| city | City of operation | String | Mumbai |
| region | Geographic region | String | West |
| state | Indian state | String | Maharashtra |
| established_year | Year dealership was established | Integer | 2005 |
| dealer_type | Type of dealership facility | String | 3S Facility |
| owner_name | Owner name | String | Owner 1 |

---

## File 2: dealer_monthly_kpi.csv / dealer_kpi_with_anomalies.csv

| Column | Description | Unit | Range | Target |
|:---|:---|:---|:---|:---|
| dealer_id | Unique dealer identifier | — | D001-D500 | — |
| month | Month of record | Date | Jan 2023 - Dec 2024 | — |
| model_wise_cr | Model-wise conversion ratio (ETBR funnel) | Percentage | 5-70 | >35% |
| sales_advisor_cr | Sales advisor-wise conversion ratio | Percentage | 3-65 | >30% |
| market_share | Market share (RTO/city wise) | Percentage | 1-40 | >15% |
| ssi | Sales Satisfaction Index | Score (50-100) | 50-100 | >85 |
| csat | Customer Satisfaction score | Rating (2.0-5.0) | 2.0-5.0 | >4.0 |
| monthly_sales | Total units sold in month | Count | 5-350 | >100 |
| booking_pipeline | Orders booked but not delivered | Count | 2-280 | >70 |
| accessories_per_car | Average accessories revenue per vehicle | INR | 500-18,000 | >5,000 |
| monthly_accessories_sales | Total accessories revenue | INR | 5,000-2,500,000 | >500,000 |
| cptv | Complaints per thousand vehicles | Count | 0.1-15 | <3 |
| tat_complaint_resolution | Turnaround time for complaint resolution | Days | 0.5-20 | <5 |

