## Dataset Characteristics
- **Seasonality:** Festival months (Oct-Nov) have 15-35% sales boost; Summer months (Apr-May) have 5-15% slowdown
- **Problem Dealers:** 60 out of 500 dealers exhibit gradual performance decline
- **Sudden Anomalies:** Random 15% chance of sudden KPI drops for problem dealers
- **Seed:** 42 (fully reproducible)